document_title: Foreign bodies in the eye: Causes, signs and dangerous complications
subsection_name: di-vat-trong-mat.json_1_Causes of foreign objects falling into the eyes
subsection_content:
Foreign objects falling into the eye can arise in many different situations.
Under the influence of the natural environment such as: wind blowing dust and sand into the eyes.; Foreign objects thrown into the eye such as: wood, metal, glass, cement or other small debris...
